<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Us</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #e0f7fa;
            color: #004d40;
            text-align: center;
        }

        header {
            background-color: #004d40;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            background-image: url('/images/header-bg.jpg');
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }

        header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 2.5em;
        }

        nav {
            display: flex;
            gap: 10px;
            margin-left: auto;
        }

        nav a {
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin: 0 10px;
            font-size: 1em;
            padding: 5px 8px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s, color 0.3s;
        }

        nav a:hover {
            background-color: #00796b;
            color: #fff;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

        main {
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .about-us {
            background-color: #b2dfdb;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            max-width: 800px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }

        .about-us h2 {
            color: #004d40;
            font-size: 2em;
        }

        .about-us p {
            color: #004d40;
            font-size: 1.1em;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }

        footer {
            background-color: #004d40;
            color: #fff;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px;
            position: fixed;
            width: 100%;
            bottom: 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>About Nature's Wonders</h1>
        <nav>
            <a href="/">Home</a>
            <a href="/about">About</a>
            <a href="/description">Description</a>
            <a href="/place">Places</a>
            <a href="/contact">Contact</a>
        </nav>
    </header>
    <main>
        <section class="about-us">
            <h2>Our Mission</h2>
            <p>At Nature's Wonders, we are dedicated to bringing you closer to the Earth's most stunning natural attractions. Our mission is to foster a deeper appreciation for the natural world by connecting you with breathtaking landscapes, serene environments, and vibrant ecosystems.</p>
            <p>By exploring these incredible destinations, you can:</p>
            <ul style="text-align: left; margin: 0 auto; display: inline-block;">
                <li>Experience the calming effects of nature on your well-being</li>
                <li>Enhance your understanding of diverse ecosystems</li>
                <li>Participate in eco-friendly tourism practices</li>
                <li>Create lasting memories with family and friends in awe-inspiring settings</li>
            </ul>
            <p>Join us on this journey to explore the world's natural wonders and make a positive impact on the environment.</p>
        </section>
    </main>
    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2024 Nature's Wonders</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
